Package: mdeditor
Title: Markdown Editor for Shiny
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Juan Pablo",
           family = "Marin Diaz",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jpmarindiaz@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Juan Pablo Marin Diaz <jpmarindiaz@gmail.com>
Description: A Shiny input widget for markdown editing using reactR and @uiw/react-md-editor.
    Provides a rich markdown editor with live preview, syntax highlighting,
    customizable themes, and extensive configuration options. Supports all
    standard markdown features including headers, lists, code blocks, tables,
    links, and more.
URL: https://github.com/jpmarindiaz/mdeditor
